
================================================================================
  Home Assistant — Claude Code Add-on
================================================================================

  Run `claude` to start a Claude Code session.

  Mapped Home Assistant paths:
    /homeassistant       HA config (configuration.yaml, automations, scenes...)
    /share               Shared folder
    /media               Media folder
    /addons              Local add-ons (read-only)
    /addon_configs       All add-on configs
    /ssl                 SSL certs (read-only)
    /backup              Backups (read-only)
    /workspace           Convenience symlinks to all of the above
    /data                Persistent add-on storage (Claude config, SSH keys)

  Helpers (use $SUPERVISOR_TOKEN automatically):
    ha-state <entity>             Get current state of an entity
    ha-call-service <d> <s> [j]   Call a service (e.g. light.turn_on)
    ha-list-entities [pattern]    List entity ids
    ha-check-config               Validate configuration.yaml
    ha-restart                    Restart Home Assistant Core
    ha-token                      Print SUPERVISOR_TOKEN

  See /workspace/CLAUDE.md for the full operator briefing.
================================================================================
